Beauteous isle, our green Taiwan.<br>
Once suffered under alien rule,<br>
Free at last to be its own.<br>
Here’s the basis of our nation:<br>
Four diverse groups in unity,<br>
Come to offer all their varied skills,<br>
For the good of all and a world at peace.<br>
